ent that God ever created."</ref><ref name=Santucci1/>。在他45分鐘的首次參選總統的公開競選演說，主要包含承諾恢復"美國夢 ... 比以前更大、與更好、與更強"，期間曾指來自[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的非法移民是「罪犯、毒販、強姦犯」<ref name=Page1/><ref name=Announcement1>[http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/06/16/trump-sets-record-for-longest-2016-gop-announcement-speech/ Trump sets record for longest 2016 GOP announcement speech] {{Wayback|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/06/16/trump-sets-record-for-longest-2016-gop-announcement-speech/ |date=20150924145609 }}. Fox News Channel, June 16, 2015</ref>。

