==== 對女性的言論爭議 ====
2015年8月，在[[霍士新聞頻道|霍士新聞頻道]]舉行的首次共和黨總統初選電視辯論中，暗指對他尖銳提問的女主播月經來潮，貶抑女性可能造成的傷害令共和黨人焦慮不已。川普過去多次在推特貼文侮辱女性，福斯新聞當家女主播[[梅根·凯利|凱利]]（Megyn Kelly）上周四在辯論會中質問他，這種男人是否適合參選總統，雙方唇槍舌劍，也讓辯論會吸引2400萬觀眾，打破美國非體育類有線電視節目最高收視率。翌日川普受訪問時稱對凱利「不怎麼尊敬」，「你可以看到血從她眼睛、從她身上其他地方流出」，暗指凱利正值生理期，莫名其妙說法引起撻伐。<ref>[http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150810/36714227/ 川普酸女主播月經來 氣走顧問] {{Wayback|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150810/36714227/ |date=20160304113756 }}，2015年8月10日，[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報 (台灣)]]</ref><ref>[http://udn.com/news/story/6813/1112001-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%92%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E8%87%AA%E8%AA%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%8F%8D%E8%A6%96%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E3%80%8D 川普拒道歉 自認「珍視女性」] {{Wayback|url=http://udn.com/news/story/6813/1112001-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%8B%92%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-%E8%87%AA%E8%AA%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%8F%8D%E8%A6%96%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E3%80%8D |date=20151227085422 }}，2015-08-11，聯合新聞網</ref>此後他並無道歉，更一度杯葛凱利有份主持的共和黨總統初選電視辯論，但後來與她達成和解並出席其節目。

2016年10月7日，華聖頓郵報發佈了一支錄於2005年的影片，片中川普和[[比利·布希|比利·布希]]（[[小布希|小布希]]的堂弟，[[老布希|老布希]]為他的伯父）高談對女性極不尊重的言論。川普在片中說他會直接親吻女性、身為明星他可以對女性做任何事、甚至抓她們的「[[鮑魚|鮑魚]]」（pussy，指[[女陰|女陰]]），並說到他如何約一名已婚女性去買家具，以試圖和對方發展關係。川普公開為此道歉，然後隨即指控[[比爾·柯林頓|比爾·柯林頓]]在任總統期間曾經多次性侵女性，還邀請被害人說明，被害人還表達支持他，他指出柯林頓所做的比他所说的更為惡劣，包含[[陸文斯基醜聞|陸文斯基醜聞]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/nbc-delayed-publication-of-lewd-trump-tape-because-of-lawsuit-fears/2016/10/08/a3c6850e-8db9-11e6-875e-2c1bfe943b66_story.html |title=NBC waited for green light from lawyers before airing Trump video |last=Farhi |first=Paul |date=2016-10-08 |newspaper=The Washington Post |language=en-US |issn=0190-8286 |access-date=2016-10-11 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010152336/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/nbc-delayed-publication-of-lewd-trump-tape-because-of-lawsuit-fears/2016/10/08/a3c6850e-8db9-11e6-875e-2c1bfe943b66_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nypost.com/2016/10/08/how-access-hollywood-unearthed-donald-trumps-vulgar-video/ |title=How 'Access Hollywood' unearthed Donald Trump's vulgar video |last=Tacopino |first=Joe |date=2016-10-08 |website=New York Post |access-date=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008102325/http://nypost.com/2016/10/08/how-access-hollywood-unearthed-donald-trumps-vulgar-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的「道歉」影片造成各方的強烈批評，包括許多共和黨員，如[[共和黨全國委員會|共和黨全國委員會]]主席[[赖因斯·普里巴斯|赖因斯·普里巴斯]]、特朗普的副總統參選人[[麥克·彭斯|麥克·彭斯]]和參議員共和黨領袖[[密契·麥康諾|密契·麥康諾]]等人都表示他們不同意川普的言論（但仍表示會繼續支持他競選總統）<ref name="McConnell">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/10/08/us/politics/how-paul-ryan-and-mitch-mcconnell-have-disavowed-trumps-words-but-not-their-support.html |title=Paul Ryan and Mitch McConnell Reject Donald Trump’s Words, Over and Over, but Not His Candidacy |first1=Larry |last1=Buchanan |first2=Alicia |last2=Parlapiano |first3=Karen |last3=Yourish |date=2016-10-08 |accessdate=2016-10-08 |newspaper=The New York Times |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008101619/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/10/08/us/politics/how-paul-ryan-and-mitch-mcconnell-have-disavowed-trumps-words-but-not-their-support.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，前總統參選人、參議員[[約翰·馬侃|約翰·馬侃]]進一步表示不會投票給川普<ref name="McCain">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/08/us/politics/presidential-election.html |title=John McCain Withdraws Support for Donald Trump After Disclosure of Recording |first=Alan |last=Rappeport |date=2016-10-08 |accessdate=2016-10-10 |newspaper=New York Times |archive-date=2016-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009203500/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/08/us/politics/presidential-election.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。共和黨全國委員會隨即取消對他的選舉支援，但繼續支持其競選<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2016/10/rnc-halts-all-victory-project-work-for-trump-229363 |title=RNC halts Victory project work for Trump |publisher= |accessdate=2016-10-11 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010225107/http://www.politico.com/story/2016/10/rnc-halts-all-victory-project-work-for-trump-229363 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2016-election/reince-priebus-says-rnc-will-stand-trump-n663996 |date=2016-10-10 |title=Lines Drawn. Reince Priebus Says RNC Will Stand by Trump |first=Leigh Ann |last=Caldwell |accessdate=2016-10-10 |publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]] |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010231220/http://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2016-election/reince-priebus-says-rnc-will-stand-trump-n663996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。眾議院議長[[保羅·萊恩|保羅·萊恩]]停止為川普拉票，選舉前一直沒有為他站台<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/nation/politics/trailguide/la-na-trailguide-updates-pence-too-is-out-at-wisconsin-event-1475944325-htmlstory.html |title=Pence, too, is out at Wisconsin event with Paul Ryan |first=Julie |last=Westfall |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=2016-10-08 |accessdate=2016-10-11 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010121225/http://www.latimes.com/nation/politics/trailguide/la-na-trailguide-updates-pence-too-is-out-at-wisconsin-event-1475944325-htmlstory.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="McConnell"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/10/politics/paul-ryan-said-he-wont-defend-donald-trump/index.html |title=Paul Ryan said he won't defend Donald Trump |first1=Manu |last1=Raju |first2=Deirdre |last2=Walsh |first3=Kevin |last3=Liptak |publisher=CNN |access-date=2016-10-10 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010163559/http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/10/politics/paul-ryan-said-he-wont-defend-donald-trump/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=USAToday-List>{{cite news |last1=Jackson |first1=David |title=Here is the list of Republicans who are not supporting Trump |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2016/10/08/donald-trump-debate-mike-crapo-mike-lee-barbara-comstock/91784714/ |accessdate=2016-10-08 |work=USA Today |date=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008203805/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2016/10/08/donald-trump-debate-mike-crapo-mike-lee-barbara-comstock/91784714/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Growth">{{cite news |last1=Yuhas |first1=Alan |title=The growing list of Republicans who have abandoned Donald Trump |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/oct/08/donald-trump-list-of-republicans-reject-support-endorsement?CMP=share_btn_tw |work=The Guardian |date=2016-10-08 |accessdate=2016-10-29 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104180308/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/oct/08/donald-trump-list-of-republicans-reject-support-endorsement?CMP=share_btn_tw |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但表明仍會投給川普。參議院中接近三分之一的共和黨員表示不會投給川普<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2016-10-11/trump-says-it-s-hard-to-do-well-with-zero-support-from-ryan |title=Trump’s Attacks on GOP Leaders Ignite Civil War Inside Party |publisher=Bloomberg News |date=2016-10-11 |accessdate=2016-10-12 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011145435/http://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2016-10-11/trump-says-it-s-hard-to-do-well-with-zero-support-from-ryan |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但也有許多共和黨的議員仍然支持川普<ref name="Support">{{cite news |last1=Scott |first1=Eugene |title=Where Republicans stand on Trump |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/08/politics/donald-trump-video-women-remarks-republicans/ |accessdate=2016-10-08 |publisher=CNN |date=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008172847/http://www.cnn.com/2016/10/08/politics/donald-trump-video-women-remarks-republicans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有數十位共和黨議員要求川普退選，讓他的副總統參選人彭斯接手<ref name="BlakeGrowingList">{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/10/07/the-gops-brutal-responses-to-the-new-trump-video-broken-down |title=Here’s the fast-growing list of Republicans calling for Donald Trump to drop out |last=Blake |first=Aaron |date=2016-10-08 |work=The Washington Post |accessdate=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2016-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008050253/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/10/07/the-gops-brutal-responses-to-the-new-trump-video-broken-down/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這個「[[更衣室|更衣室]]談話」也根本不是在更衣室，言論也直接引來運動員的批評，還說川普醜化更衣室的形象，並表明他們從來沒有聽過在男性更衣室有過與川普類似的言論。

2016年10月12日起，川普陸續被至少12名女性指控曾性騷女性，包含30多年前在飛機上性騷、2001年沒有通知就闖入美國小姐選拔賽的更衣室、2005年趁其妻不在強吻女記者等。對此川普全部反駁，指是民主黨候選人希拉蕊、親希拉蕊媒體和游說家所為及收買，是他們試圖要阻止他進入[[白宮|白宮]]的一個手段，並表示將会向他們提出誹謗指控及法律訴訟。

==== 多次用推特辱罵各種對象 ====
而上述言論被[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]整理後，在2016年10月23日刊登兩大頁，顯示他用[[推特|推特]]至少批評過282個特定的攻擊對象，包含[[希拉蕊·柯林頓|希拉蕊·柯林頓]]、[[美國|美國]]、[[英國|英國]]掩飾國內[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]極端主義的問題、[[伊朗|伊朗]]在背後搞一堆恐怖主義事情、[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]、共和黨重要人物及民主黨重要人士、批評[[梅克爾|梅克爾]]的[[歐洲移民危機|歐洲移民危機]]政策會毀滅[[德國|德國]]及[[歐洲|歐洲]]，不只如此批評政治人物，還不乏批評奧運選手「不是好人」、演員揮高爾夫球桿「不夠運動風」等等。<ref>{{cite news|title=The 282 People, Places and Things Donald Trump Has Insulted on Twitter: A Complete List|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/01/28/upshot/donald-trump-twitter-insults.html?_r=0|accessdate=2016-10-23|agency=|date=2016-10-23|archive-date=2016-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023074450/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2016/01/28/upshot/donald-trump-twitter-insults.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

